bibliothek.gui.dock.layout

Class PropertyTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.gui.dock.layout.PropertyTransformer

  • public class PropertyTransformer
extends Object
    A PropertyTransformer can read and write instances of DockableProperty , assuming that a factory is installed for the property.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
